original_title: Janelle Monáe: Live at iTunes Festival 2013
overview: Janelle Monáe hit the 2013 iTunes Festival stage, and, as usual, the ‘Electric Lady’ songstress delivered. Monáe was cool and effortless in their performance of ‘Q.U.E.E.N.’ Never straying too far from their black and white striped mic stand, Monáe performed not only their vocals, but stood in for partner-in-crime Erykah Badu’s raps as well.
title: Janelle Monáe: Live at iTunes Festival 2013
